{
  "texts": [
    "CKLE predictive model preserves the global model interpretability, which can provide the feature importance by the attention score.",
    "The interpretability is a very essential aspect when we build the medical AI models.",
    "In this paper, we distill the knowledge from LLM into the predictive model, which is a type of Transformer.",
    "The interpretability of Transformer can be represented as the attention score for each input features.",
    "The feature importance can show which feature plays an important role in the predictions."
  ]
}